Possibly related to scala/bug#4426 since that's what I was reducing when I ran into this one.  Someday I hope to find fewer than one new bug per attempted bugfix...
```scala
object Main {
  def f = {
    class A {
      val x = {
        object cc
        ()
      }
    }
    new A
  }
}
```
